summary: This document is a letter dated November 13, 2025, from INVO Fertility, Inc. to James Goren of JAG Multi Investments LLC, regarding the extension of maturity dates for certain demand notes and a reduction in the warrant exercise price. If INVO pays $100,000 by November 31, 2025, the maturity date of the notes will extend to December 31, 2025, and the warrant exercise price will reduce to $0.75 per share.
